T02D3176:193a-1: badzr'a nam ka s'a dha nam//
T02D3176:193a-3: rdo rje lus med kyi sgrub thabs /
T02D3176:193a-4: sngar bshad pa'i cho ga'i rim pas stong pa nyid
T02D3176:193a-5: bsgoms pa'i rjes thogs la sna tshogs padma dang nyi
T02D3176:193a-6: ma la sa bon gyi yi ge bam ser po
T02D3176:193a-7: yongs su gyur pa las rje btsun 'jam dpal rdo
T02D3176:193a-8: rje lus med du bdag nyid skad cig gis mngon
T02D3176:193a-10: sku mdog ser po zhal gsum pa /
T02D3176:193a-11: phyag drug pa ral pa dang ldan pa /
T02D3176:193a-12: lo brgyad gnyis kyi chad sgeg bag dang ldan pa /
T02D3176:193a-13: zhabs g-yas pa bskum pa ste /
T02D3176:193a-14: g-yas kyi phyag gsum na ral gri dang mda' dang me long bsnams pa'o //
T02D3176:193b-0: @193b g-yon gyi phyag gsum na ni autpala dang gzhu dang shing mya ngan med bsnams pa'o //
T02D3176:193b-1: lha rdzas kyi rgyan dang na bza' mdzes par gyur
T02D3176:193b-2: pa mi bskyod pa dbu rgyan la gnas par bsgoms
T02D3176:193b-3: la / smyo ba'i sbyor bas bsgom par bya ba'o //
T02D3176:193b-4: de ltar yang lcags kyus mkhal khung phug la shing mya ngan med kyi snying la gtol bar bya'o //
T02D3176:193b-5: ral gris ni bsdigs par bya zhing bsgrub bya la me long gis bstan par bya ba'o //
T02D3176:193b-6: de nas autpala las rkang pa rnam par bcings la
T02D3176:193b-7: skra grol ba myos shing bskam par gyur pa drang
T02D3176:193b-9: aom che ge mo khug manydzu gho sha hr'i: dza: zhes bya'o //
